INGREDIENTS 
1.5 cup (100 grams) milk powder, unsweetened
1 cup (60 grams) maida / plain flour
1 tsp baking powder
4 tbsp ghee / clarified butter
milk (for kneading)
ghee or oil (for frying)
or sugar syrup:
4 cup sugar
4 cup water
4 cardamom
0.5 tsp saffron / kesar
2 tsp lemon juice
2 tsp rose water